                           </h6>
                           <div id="collapseOneV1" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" data-bs-parent="#accordionLeft">
                              <div class="accordion-body">The best times to travel to India is usually from October till March, when the weather is pleasant in most parts of the country. Now, travel during monsoon months (July – September) is also possible, as appropriate facilities are being provided at places that present a good tourism opportunity during this time (such as Goa, the Western Ghats, Kerala, etc.). </div>
